[0.002, "o", "\u001b[1m{\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[32m\"result\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m{\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[32m\"message\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"Successfully retrieved list of all posts\"\u001b[0m,\r\n    \u001b[32m\"endpoint\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts\"\u001b[0m,\r\n    \u001b[32m\"status\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"The posts data should be visible on the current page as JSON \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mformat containing an array of post objects with fields like userId, id, title, \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mand body\"\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[1m}\u001b[0m,\r\n  \u001b[32m\"steps_taken\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[1;36m7\u001b[0m,\r\n  \u001b[32m\"history\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m[\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[1m{\u001b[0m\r\n      \u001b[32m\"step\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[1;36m0\u001b[0m,\r\n      \u001b[32m\"instruction\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m{\u001b[0m\r\n        \u001b[32m\"action\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"click\"\u001b[0m,\r\n        \u001b[32m\"selector\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"a\u001b[0m\u001b[32m\"\u001b[0m,\r\n        \u001b[32m\"reason\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"Click on the /posts link to retrieve all posts from the \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32msystem\"\u001b[0m\r\n      \u001b[1m}\u001b[0m\r\n    \u001b[1m}\u001b[0m,\r\n    \u001b[1m{\u001b[0m\r\n      \u001b[32m\"step\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[1;36m0\u001b[0m,\r\n      \u001b[32m\"error\"\u001b[0m: \u001b[32m\"Page.click: Timeout 5000ms exceeded.\\nCall log:\\n  - waiting for\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32mlocator\u001b[0m\u001b[32m(\u001b[0m\u001b[32m\\\"a\u001b["]
